mcfarland & lt ; mcfe > to buy petromin & lt ; ptro > mcfarland energi inc said it board and that of petromin corp have approv a definit agreement for mcfarland to acquir petromin in an exchang of stock . mcfarland said it would exchang one common share for each 5.4 petromin share . mcfarland said former holder of petromin will have a 25 pct interest in the combin compani . the merger is still subject to approv by sharehold of both compani .